-- Gerar código de verificação para dreatnu@yahoo.com
INSERT INTO codigosAcessoGestante (gestanteId, codigo, expiresAt, usado)
SELECT 
  id,
  '654321' as codigo,
  DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 15 MINUTE) as expiresAt,
  0 as usado
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'dreatnu@yahoo.com'
LIMIT 1;
